# System Flow Diagrams - Knowledge Sharing Tech Community

## Overview
This document contains Mermaid flow diagrams for all major system flows in the Knowledge Sharing Tech Community platform.

---

## 1. Authentication Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Login Request] --> B{Authentication Method}
    B -->|Email/Password| C[Validate Credentials]
    B -->|OAuth Provider| D[OAuth Redirect]
    B -->|SSO| E[Enterprise SSO]
    
    C --> F{Credentials Valid?}
    D --> G[OAuth Token Exchange]
    E --> H[SSO Validation]
    
    F -->|No| I[Return Error]
    F -->|Yes| J[Generate JWT Token]
    G --> K{OAuth Success?}
    H --> L{SSO Valid?}
    
    K -->|No| I
    K -->|Yes| J
    L -->|No| I
    L -->|Yes| J
    
    J --> M[Update Last Login]
    M --> N[Check Trust Score]
    N --> O{Trust Score > Threshold?}
    O -->|No| P[Restricted Access]
    O -->|Yes| Q[Full Access]
    
    P --> R[Return Limited Token]
    Q --> S[Return Full Token]
    I --> T[Login Failed Response]
    R --> U[Redirect to Dashboard]
    S --> U
    T --> V[Redirect to Login]
```

