## 2. Content Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Creates Content] --> B[Content Validation]
    B --> C{Validation Passed?}
    C -->|No| D[Return Validation Errors]
    C -->|Yes| E[Check Trust Score]
    
    E --> F{Trust Score Sufficient?}
    F -->|No| G[Queue for Review]
    F -->|Yes| H[Auto-Approve]
    
    G --> I[Moderator Review]
    I --> J{Moderator Decision}
    J -->|Approve| K[Publish Content]
    J -->|Reject| L[Notify Rejection]
    J -->|Request Changes| M[Return for Revision]
    
    H --> K
    K --> N[Update Trust Score]
    N --> O[Notify Followers]
    O --> P[Update Search Index]
    P --> Q[Log Activity]
    
    L --> R[Update Trust Score]
    M --> S[Notify User]
    Q --> T[Content Published]
    S --> U[User Revises Content]
    U --> B
```

