## 3. Report Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Reports Content/User] --> B[Report Validation]
    B --> C{Valid Report?}
    C -->|No| D[Reject Report]
    C -->|Yes| E[Categorize Report Type]
    
    E --> F{Report Category}
    F -->|Spam| G[Low Priority Queue]
    F -->|Harassment| H[High Priority Queue]
    F -->|Quality| I[Medium Priority Queue]
    F -->|Security| J[Urgent Priority Queue]
    
    G --> K[Auto-Review Possible]
    H --> L[Immediate Human Review]
    I --> M[Standard Review Process]
    J --> N[Emergency Review]
    
    K --> O{Auto-Action Possible?}
    O -->|Yes| P[Apply Auto-Action]
    O -->|No| Q[Assign Moderator]
    
    L --> R[Assign Senior Moderator]
    M --> Q
    N --> S[Assign Safety Team]
    
    P --> T[Notify Reporter]
    Q --> U[Moderator Investigation]
    R --> U
    S --> U
    
    U --> V{Investigation Result}
    V -->|No Action| W[Close Report]
    V -->|Warning| X[Issue Warning]
    V -->|Content Removal| Y[Remove Content]
    V -->|Account Action| Z[Apply Account Penalty]
    
    W --> AA[Update Trust Scores]
    X --> AA
    Y --> AA
    Z --> AA
    
    AA --> BB[Notify All Parties]
    BB --> CC[Log for Pattern Analysis]
```

