## 5. Trust Scoring Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Action] --> B[Action Classification]
    B --> C{Action Type}
    C -->|Positive| D[Calculate Positive Impact]
    C -->|Negative| E[Calculate Negative Impact]
    C -->|Neutral| F[No Score Change]
    
    D --> G[Quality Assessment]
    E --> H[Severity Assessment]
    F --> I[Update Activity Log]
    
    G --> J{Quality Score}
    J -->|High| K[Large Score Increase]
    J -->|Medium| L[Medium Score Increase]
    J -->|Low| M[Small Score Increase]
    
    H --> N{Severity Level}
    N -->|Low| O[Small Score Decrease]
    N -->|Medium| P[Medium Score Decrease]
    N -->|High| Q[Large Score Decrease]
    N -->|Critical| R[Major Score Decrease]
    
    K --> S[Apply Score Change]
    L --> S
    M --> S
    O --> S
    P --> S
    Q --> S
    R --> S
    
    S --> T[Update Trust Score]
    T --> U{Trust Score Threshold Check}
    U -->|Below Warning| V[Apply Restrictions]
    U -->|Below Critical| W[Apply Severe Restrictions]
    U -->|Above Recovery| X[Restore Privileges]
    U -->|Normal Range| Y[Maintain Current Status]
    
    V --> Z[Notify User]
    W --> Z
    X --> Z
    Y --> AA[Continue Normal Operation]
    
    Z --> BB[Log Trust Score Change]
    I --> BB
    BB --> CC[Update User Status]
```

